author: Shaun M
title: Mike Will Made It - On The Come Up Feat. Big Sean
text:
4 MAKE IT STOP Mike Will and Big Sean link up on the track " On The Come Up." 
On March 24, Mike Will Made-It will release his much-anticipated Ransom 2 . Following last week's sizzling "Gucci On My," featuring 21 Savage , YG and Migos , Mike Will dropped "On The Come Up," featuring Big Sean . 
While Mike Will samples and skews an opera singer's vocals in an endless loop, Big Sean goes hard on this track. Paired with a deep 808 bass, "On The Come Up" is one of those summer tracks that bad boys like to blast on their speakers when they want to stun respectable citizens downtown. Big Sean spits that he's out to get his piece of a bigger pie. Like he hasn't had enough yet. This might end up being one of the best bangers on Ransom 2 . 
Listen to "On The Come Up" right here.
